 so start making more realistic drawings 

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:05.300
 I was doing better and better in the drawing practicing daily 

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:11.860
 I was always shy and calm and that's why they bothered me at the lyceum 

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:18.080
 at that point in my life I did not understand why some are bad with others 

